{"tid":656196,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普叫沙拿唔好再插水","createTime":"2018-05-07T04:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:34:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11c7d1299a62b78aa3c31d5ddcc1efa10051d642","tid":656196,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/4/594/21332719594/21342159443_600x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F4%2F594%2F21332719594%2F21342159443_600x390.jpg&h=c995faa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=w0NGSwCg9T%2FhjTbcvAW1SQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=329b93f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】利物浦領隊高普在周日賽後，勸誡翼鋒穆罕默德沙拿不要再插水。<br />\n<br />\n在周日英超以0:1敗走車路士，利物浦大紅人穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah）在上半場疑似跟對方中堅加利卡希爾接觸而倒地，被球證認為是插水而罰黃牌。<br />\n<br />\n高普表示：「這是插水，或者他一直等待被侵犯，這不是我想看到的，也不是他想做的。在其他所有情況，沙拿經常被侵犯，這也是不應該的，但你就是要面對這情況。」<br />\n<br />\n在早前7場轟入11球的火熱走勢後，沙拿近3場都顆粒無收，高普說：「他要做得更好，而且可以做得更好，之後就會再度入球了，這是毫無疑問的事。這不關乎他有沒有空間的問題，他可以在沒有空間下踢球，只是明顯地今天不能。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"73c0924a108a46d15af329991d41cd780e9d1a40","tid":656196,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"痢狗文化"},{"pid":"ad6568ebc6f86913eede24c0557d1225244e35ad","tid":656196,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"73c0924a108a46d15af329991d41cd780e9d1a40","tid":656196,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"痢狗文化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"插完水俾領隊開口話?"},{"pid":"bda9a5bbdc444bddecd3461b0df931e47d1406f5","tid":656196,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c78747fc710fec3f1c129c94